name: Roots 18
description: This project is growing and taking many forms from M.M.M. to Ganimation to Stills as the condition I was afflicted with, from satisfaction of creativity to self doubt and desire of changes,Unbridled optimism to Pessimistic outlook . Using what I see through my window looking at the forest I live in to create text prompt, these GAN images created using vqgan-clip are the result of different stages from the burnout I was living. A project meant to get me back to my roots as an artist and a permaculturist.
